In a message dated 11/2/01 11:20:46 AM Pacific Standard Time, rdahl@... 
writes:

<< (Spasstik picked different targets however. His duel laser cannons
 targeting the running Groove. Both let out a laser beam towards the
 Protectobot. Then his rear anti neutrino grenade launchers aimed
 upwards, arcking off two grenades into the middle of the Protectobot
 formation, as the Decepticon wolf snarled with fury.)
  >>

The Protectobots:

Groove was struck by the laser beams, tearing into his form and causing him 
to stumble.  He crashed to the ground in pain.

The grenades hit in the middle of the Protectobot formation, sending the 
Autobots flying back several feet and crashing to the ground, dazed and 
slightly fried.
